        Parameters:
        reportId -
        koie_name - The koie name
        status - The status of the report. Tells us whether everything is okay, something is forgotten, or some equipment is broken/missing
        startdate - The start date of the koie stay
        enddate - The end date of the koie stay
        smoke_detector - Whether or not the smoke detector is working
        wood - How much wood there is left
        remarks_of_defects - String of equipment that is missing/not working separated with a comma
        forgotten - Tells us if something is forgotten
        comments - Comments on what is forgotten/random comments
        timeStamp - Time of report delivery.
